message.text:
ICYMI: FEU SAGA in this year's TamHunt 2025, #HabiSangPaglainlain! 🏳️‍🌈

The FEU Sexuality and Gender Alliance proudly brought the spirit of South Cotabato to TamHunt 2025, celebrating culture, identity, and unity. 

We weren’t just there to perform, we came to find the next sewers of change. 🧶

Ito ang iyong simula patungo sa #PasinayaNgPaglaya. Ready to be a part of the cuntiest and sassiest FEU SAGA journey? 🌈

Special thanks to: 
Corazon Factor Robin 

#FEUSAGA 
#TAMHunt2025

Caption by Axl Benedict
Publication Material by Denz Alcantara
